title: North Korean cheerleaders perform on the sidelines of Winter Olympics
text:
North Korean cheerleaders perform on the sidelines of Winter Olympics Saturday, February 17, 2018 - 01:11 
The team were watched by an enthusiastic crowd of South Koreans and foreign visitors to the games. Rough cut (no reporter narration) ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
